<https://w3id.org/ppon/lppo#photobiologyClass> <https://w3id.org/ppon/bppo#description> "The required measurement methods and the calculation methodology are set in the harmonized standard IEC 62471:2009 / CIE S009:2006 „Photobiological safety of lamps and lamp systems“. The standard divides the sources of incoherent optical radiation into four groups: in the Exempt Group (no photobiological risk) and the Risk Groups 1 to 3 with increasing hazard potential."@en .
